    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 14</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 26 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 14 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 30</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique is identical to Rasengan (p327), except as noted above, and the sphere is much greater, becoming a Force effect. On hit, the target is stunned for 1d4+1 rounds rather than being knocked back.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> As Rasengan, except you can empower up to 20d8 damage total, and the Perform Requirements do not increase when empowering.</p>\n\n",
